OL,11,F16, died in the Ely area on Monday.    
OL,13,FPolice and Crime Commissioner Alun     
OL,14,FMichael initially said police did not  
OL,15,Fchase the boys but CCTV showed their   
OL,16,Felectric bike was followed by police.  
